<title>USA: 360 says board authorizes 3-mln shr buyback.</title>
<headline>360 says board authorizes 3-mln shr buyback.</headline>
<dateline>CHICAGO 1997-04-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>360 Communications Co said its board authorized the repurchase of up to three million shares of the company's common stock through May 1, 1998.</p>
<p>The shares may be purchased from time to time on the open market at prevailing prices, subject to market conditions, said 360, an independent company since its March 1996 spinoff from Sprint Corp</p>
<p>The wireless voice and data services company has about 123.3 million shares outstanding.</p>
<p>((--Chicago Newsdesk 312-408-8787))</p>
